
Documentary on the Cradle to Cradle philosophy

Video at http://www.developmentcrossing.com/video/documentary-cradle-to-crade


=Description=


"This documentary outlines the concept of Cradle to Cradle or Waste = Food. It offers a revolutionary paradigm shift on the way we perceive, design and produce materials and products.
Nike, Ford, China and clothing/design companies each offer their results and experiences with implementing and 'living' the philosophy."
(http://www.developmentcrossing.com/video/documentary-cradle-to-crade)



